{"data":{"info":{"name":"James Jarvis","title":"Software Engineer, Explorer","socials":[{"icon":"linkedin-in","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrjamesjarvis/","text":"Connect with me!"},{"icon":"github","url":"https://github.com/jamesjarvis","text":"Critique my code!"},{"icon":"keybase","url":"https://keybase.io/jamesjarvis","text":"View my proofs!"},{"icon":"instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jamjarvis/","text":"Follow me!"},{"icon":"youtube","url":"https://www.youtube.com/c/JamesJarvis1998","text":"Watch my videos!"}]},"bio":{"html":"<p>Hi, I'm James.\nI'm currently on industrial placement in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silicon_Valley\">Silicon Valley</a> at <a href=\"https://www.cisco.com\">Cisco Systems</a> in between my studies at the <a href=\"https://www.kent.ac.uk\">University of Kent</a>, and between my day to day work I actively contribute to my ongoing projects.\nIn my spare time you'll probably find me hopping on a cheap plane somewhere, camera in my hand and in search for an adventure.\nFeel free to reach out to me below regarding professional work, or just for a chat!\nAlso, if you're into that sort of stuff, you can find my public keys <a href=\"https://keybase.pub/jamesjarvis/keys/\">here</a>.</p>"},"avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"avatar":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":200,"height":200,"src":"/static/312a750d0aa123cbd18bc13c8131a093/511b7/avatar.jpg","srcSet":"/static/312a750d0aa123cbd18bc13c8131a093/511b7/avatar.jpg 1x,\n/static/312a750d0aa123cbd18bc13c8131a093/5c0c2/avatar.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/312a750d0aa123cbd18bc13c8131a093/0fa17/avatar.jpg 2x,\n/static/312a750d0aa123cbd18bc13c8131a093/70cc3/avatar.jpg 3x"}}}}}